					<description><![CDATA[<p>Smoke doesn’t check borders. You learn that fast on a fireline, watching a fire run...</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://earth911.com/home-garden/guest-idea-the-wildfire-season-youre-not-prepared-for/">Guest Idea: The Wildfire Season You&#8217;re Not Prepared For</a> appeared first on <a href="https://earth911.com">Earth911</a>.</p>
